        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Retirees Sustainable Investment Policies Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires retirement and employee benefit plans to establish and follow a sustainable investment policy, including policies relating to the corporate governance practices, labor and human rights practices, and the environmental risks of the entities receiving investments.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
